title: Pier Luigi Nervi (Architecture Art Ebook).pdf
description:
G. Braziller | 1960 | Pdf | Eng | 128 pages | 19.2 MB

WHEN PIER LUIGI NERVI speaks of his work, it is with matter-of-fact modesty.
To questions about the technical innovations of the unprecedented structures that he
has built for almost half a century, he replies, in a tone of slight surprise: "It was simple ... the obvious solution ... the logical thing to do."
